927
00:55:42,444 --> 00:55:44,969
If you marry him,
let me be your lover.

928
00:55:45,147 --> 00:55:46,739
- You?
- Yes, you'll tell me stories.

929
00:55:47,082 --> 00:55:49,983
It's very interesting.
