951
00:56:48,644 --> 00:56:51,545
Too pity.
I hoped on your intuition.

952
00:56:51,713 --> 00:56:55,205
You know, sometimes
I feel like a poor cat.

953
00:56:55,384 --> 00:56:57,511
- I know.
